{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3419330/extras/HEADER_IDEA_ENG.png?t=1739639288\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>IslaNode: Rescue Signal</strong> takes players on a survival adventure like no other, set on a deserted island with nothing but natural resources and your wits. Stranded alone, you\u2019ll need to explore, gather materials, and use a unique node-based crafting system to transform basic elements into survival tools.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this demo version of the game, you will find yourself on a small island where you will need to complete various objectives, such as cutting down a tree and crafting tools, in order to complete the level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3419330/extras/HEADER_CRAFTING_ENG.png?t=1739639288\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3419330/extras/crafting_1.gif?t=1739639288\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combine world resources to craft.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3419330/extras/HEADER_BUILDING_ENG.png?t=1739639288\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3419330/extras/building_1.gif?t=1739639288\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Building allows you to create more complex shapes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3419330/extras/HEADER_OBJECTIVE_ENG.png?t=1739639288\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3419330/extras/building_2.gif?t=1739639288\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The ultimate goal? Construct a towering lighthouse to signal for help and secure your escape. Each resource you gather, from wood to stone, plays a crucial role in building a sturdy, weather-resistant tower as you face the challenges of the island environment. With vibrant, cartoony visuals and an intuitive crafting interface, <strong><i>IslaNode</i></strong> combines the thrill of survival with the satisfaction of creative construction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"LAUNCH GAME","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3419330/42c2543837936390d5ad22191bad58a9bc82b9c9.jpg"},{"name":"Build 5m up","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3419330/21b41fdff5ab8b1e15847cc828c0dd62676b9904.jpg"},{"name":"CRAFT AN AXE","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3419330/5bd33eaf361ad01f235d5e74e78b4dc87bd7e60c.jpg"}],"total":3},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3419330/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739639288","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3419330/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739639288","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3419330/f8787d65bc9ecffbafc289c22e0635a27c28cd65/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739639288","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3419330/f8787d65bc9ecffbafc289c22e0635a27c28cd65/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739639288","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/